These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: pumpkin, mango, peach, nectarine, artichoke, corn, peas
There are 7 different nationalities: indian, egyptian, italian, british, polish, chinese, pakistani
 1. the person eating peach is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating nectarine is not the chinese##6
 3. the indian is on the left of the person eating mango##1
 4. the pakistani is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
 5. the person eating artichoke is on the left or right of the person eating peas##3
 6. the indian is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 7. the person eating corn is somewhere between the person eating mango and the egyptian##7
 8. the egyptian is on the left of the pakistani##1
 9. the british is somewhere between the person eating artichoke and the italian##7
10. the italian is on the left or right of the indian##3
11. the polish is on the far left##1
12. the person eating nectarine is somewhere to the left of the pakistani##5
13. the person eating nectarine is somewhere to the right of the person eating corn##5
14. the person eating peas is somewhere to the right of the person eating artichoke##5
15. the person eating artichoke is the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Food          | peach    | pumpkin    | mango | corn | nectarine | artichoke    | peas |
| Nationality   | polish | indian | italian  | chinese   | british    | egyptian | pakistani |

