.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There 7 different types of food: pineapple, pumpkin, lettuce, orange, tomato, blueberry, cucumber
The people have 7 different hobbies: woodworking, magic-tricks, photography, filmmaking, fishing, baking, collecting
 1. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere between the person eating cucumber and the person eating pumpkin##7
 2. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person eating orange##1
 3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
 5. the person eating pineapple is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##7
 6. the person eating blueberry is somewhere between the person eating orange and the person who's hobby is photography##7
 7. the person eating tomato is somewhere between the person eating orange and the person eating pumpkin##7
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the left of the person eating tomato##5
10. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5
11. the person who's hobby is baking is not the person eating cucumber##6
12. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
13. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person eating orange##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Food    | cucumber  | lettuce | blueberry | orange | pineapple     | tomato | pumpkin  |
| Hobby   | photography | baking | magic-tricks  | collecting  | fishing | filmmaking      | woodworking |

