.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: singing, writing, fishing, chess, baking, gardening, hiking
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: rock, pop, disco, funk, techno, r&b, indie
 1. the fan of indie is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the fan of disco##2
 2. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the right of the fan of pop##5
 3. the fan of pop is not the person who's hobby is chess##6
 4. the fan of rock is somewhere to the right of the fan of r&b##5
 5. the fan of rock is between the fan of r&b and the person who's hobby is baking##2
 6. the fan of disco is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
 9. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere between the fan of techno and the fan of indie##7
10. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
11. the person who's hobby is baking is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is baking is not the fan of rock##6
13. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's hobby is baking##7
14. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
15. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
16. the person who's hobby is baking is not the fan of r&b##6
17. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
18. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
19. the fan of rock is somewhere to the left of the fan of techno##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |    4    |       5       |     6     |      7      |
| Hobby         | singing | writing | gardening | baking  | fishing | chess | hiking |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | r&b       | rock   | techno | funk           | indie     | disco     |

