 7. the person driving the train is somewhere between the person driving the roller and the person driving the boat##7
 8. the person who's sport is bikeing is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##5
10. the person who's sport is climbing is in an even position##4
11. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is cycling##7
12. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
13. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
14. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the left of the person driving the airplane##5
